devdoc.author: Juan Castellon
devdoc.details: Every time the user creates a new company a new instance of  this Company contract is going to be created. It will store all data related with the company.

constructor.details: Default constructor where the owner and all attributes of a company are set.

params.anOwner: the address of this company's owner.
params.companyDid: string with company's DID (not used at the moment)
params.companyName: string with the name of the company.
params.uPortAdd: address with uPort Ethr address (not used for now)

modifyOwner(address).details: This function will allow the owner of the contract to transfer  ownership to a new owner.

terminateCompany().details: this method will be executed to terminate a company. At the moment It's not fully implemented yet.
